<p>Whitney:</p>
<p>Try opening parallels. Then choose "File" -&gt; "Check for updates". If there is an update available, download and install it (I assume you have administrator privileges on your machine). After a restart, try Parallels again and let me know how it goes.</p>
<p>Tom</p>
<p>This approach is recommended here:&nbsp;https://discussions.apple.com/thread/3190005?start=0&amp;tstart=0</p>